CHICAGO — Canadian radio
guests customers partly.
“There are more people coming into Canada than leaving it.
We welcome these young people
as Canada‘s new life blood,"
broadcasts declare.
Dick camp, Grinnell sopho<
more from West morris Hall,
spent several days during Christmas in Toronto, Canada, with
